---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About RNS Videomedia"
	description="35 years of East Coast equestrian eventing coverage — every phase, every venue."
	pubDate={new Date('2024-01-01')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		RNS Videomedia has been on the rail at East Coast equestrian events for over 35 years.
		Mark and Lou Ann have footage from every major USEA-recognized eventing venue on the
		East Coast, and relationships with hundreds of competitors who trust them to capture
		dressage, cross-country, and show jumping exactly as it happens.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is where that knowledge lands — show coverage, venue spotlights, competitor
		profiles, and a ground-level view of the East Coast eventing circuit. If you've competed
		at Plantation Field, Waredaca, or Fair Hill, there's a good chance we've been there
		with a camera.
	</p>

	<p>
		<em>On Course</em> is produced by Reel Neet Solutions, the automation layer connecting
		RNS Videomedia's footage library, show data, and client relationships into a unified
		system. Every competitor at every show gets a complete, personalized video package —
		every phase of the event, custom graphics included.
	</p>

	<p>
		Questions about video packages or coverage? Reach out directly. We cover what we cover,
		and we know this world well.
	</p>
</Layout>
